Olawale Shodeinde in Abeokuta The Ogun House of Assembly has pass resolution suspending all traditional rulers appointed and promoted  from February, 2019 till May 28, 2019 Also suspended are all Local council and LCDA political officers to allow for investigation on allegations leveled against them on gross misconduct and misappropriation of public fund. The assembly thereafter ordered that the LG and LCDA Chairman and House Leader hand over the affairs of the councils to the HOLGA and appear before the assembly on the 7th of June, 2019.